Package org.example

Class CustomApplianceSet

java.lang.Object
org.example.CustomApplianceSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<ElectricAppliance>, Collection<ElectricAppliance>, Set<ElectricAppliance>
public class CustomApplianceSet extends Object implements Set<ElectricAppliance>
Custom collection class that implements the Set interface for ElectricAppliance objects. It uses an array as its internal data structure to store unique elements. The initial capacity is 15, and the capacity increases by 30% when full.
